title: #119: The Black Cube with Magnora 7
description:
Welcome to another amazing episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode the guys welcome the creator of Said it.net, Magnora 7, back to the show to discuss the cloak and dagger world of the Black Cube Creative Intelligence. This episode is mind-blowing. Thank you so much for all of your support and we hope to see you at one of our upcoming live events.
Sept 5th- The Comedy Store at m8pm
Sept 14th and 15th- The Corner Comedy in Niagara Falls Canada
Oct 12th: The Punchline Philly
Oct 14th: The Syracuse Funny Bone
Nov 3rd: The Secret Group in Houston
Nov 4th: Stateside Theatre in Austin Texas
